{"title":"今年我十岁","authors":["赵宗宪"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":6,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年我十岁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西藏扎囊县中学"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵宗宪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爷爷十岁做差役，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寒冬掉进拉萨河。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿爸十岁当奴隶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做牛做马腰背驼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年我也整十岁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"背着书包去上课。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学写字，学唱歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学做游戏开火车。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}